'''hucklebuck''' (''plural:'' '''hucklebucks''')

#A redneck, hillbilly, or otherwise culturally backwards person, usually descended from the [[Amish]] or [[Pennsylvania Dutch]] and residing in central Pennsylvania.

#A slang term for a sexual position where the female is on her back with her knees up next to her head and against the ground, and the male can achieve maximum penetration by repeated pounding.